Welcome to the **Material Nodes** example level! This Content Example is designed to familiarize you with the different inputs available on Materials, demonstrating how each one can be used.



[INCLUDE:Resources\ContentExamples\ExampleLevelOverview#ExampleLevel]

As with all Content Examples, this level is meant to be interactive. With any of the Material samples you see displayed, you can select them with the left mouse button, and then preview their Material by **double-clicking** on the Material in the **Details** panel listed under **Element 0** as shown below.

